AfDB tinye ego $50m na AFC iji kwalite ikike mmepe na Afrịka 
Ego nhatanha ahụ na AFC na-agbasawanye ikike onye nwe ihe na AFC, ma sorokwa ego nha anya na AFC site n'African Re-Insurance Corporation na Republic nke Ghana 
Ụlọakụ African Development Bank etinyela $50m na Africa Finance Corporation iji kwalite mmepe na kọntinent ahụ. 
Akụ nke AfDB na-enyere ụlọọrụ abụọ ahụ aka ime ka mmepe dị na kọntinent ahụ site n'imeziwanye oghere nke itinye ego, mmejupụta njikọta, nnyefe ihe ọmụma na mmepe ikike maka ọdịmma nke Afrịka. 
Nkwupụta sitere n'ụlọọrụ ahụ, nke gosipụtara nke a, kwuru na mgbakwụnye nke AfDB dịka onye na-ahụ maka ego mezuru atụmatụ ya nke idozi ụkọ akụrụngwa Africa na ọrụ ikwupụta atụmatụ AfDB iji nye aka belata ịda ogbenye, 
Meziwanye ọnọdụ obibi ndụ ndị Africa ma na-achịkọta ego maka maka mmepe akụnaụba n'obodo. 
Nkwupụta ahụ kwuru, "Ego nhatanha na AFC na-agbatịkwu ọnụọgụgụ nke AFC, na-esokwa ntinye ego na AFC site n'African Re-Insurance Corporation na Republic nke Ghana. 
Dịka ihe ntinye ego nhatanha, AfDB ga-enwe nnọchiteanya na kọmitii ndị isi AFC". 
